2. Once the installation is done close the program
3. Run patch.exe and select the main trillian.exe (should be in &lt;install dir&gt;trillian.exe)
4. You may also optionally remove some ASTRA network nags by clicking next in the patcher and selecting astra.dll (should be in &lt;install dir&gt;pluginsastra.dll). The patch fools trillian into believing that you are infact connected to the ASTRA network, but in reality you aren&amp;#039;t
5. Enjoy the program!

